Kinetic_Shield.help: Kinetic Shield creates a harmonic Energy Aura that can deflect physical attacks. Your Defense to Smashing and Lethal attacks is increased as weapons and powers like bullets, blades and punches tend to deflect off the shield. Kinetic Shield also grants you good resistance to Defense Debuffs. The Energy based nature of Kinetic Shield also offers some minimal Defense to Energy attacks. Kinetic Shield also adds an Elusivity defense bonus to Smashing, Lethal, and Energy Attacks in PVP zones. Recharge: Fast
Kinetic_Shield.shortHelp: Toggle: Self +DEF(Smashing, Lethal, Energy), Res(DeBuff DEF)
Kinetic_Shield.attackerHit: Your Kinetic Shield increased your Defense to Lethal, Smashing, and to some degree, Energy attacks.

Kinetic_Dampening.help: Your ability to channel energy makes you naturally resistant to Energy, Negative Energy, Lethal, Smashing and Toxic damage. Additionally, the user gains a moderate level of resistance to slow effects. This power is always on and costs no Endurance.
Kinetic_Dampening.shortHelp: Auto: Self +Res (Energy, Negative, Toxic, Lethal, Smashing, Slow)

Power_Shield.help: This Power Shield creates a Electro-Magnetic shield around you that can deflect non-physical attacks. Your Defense to Fire, Cold, Energy and Negative Energy attacks is increased as these attacks are reflected or refracted off the shield. Power Shield also grants you good resistance to Defense Debuffs. Power Shield also adds Psionic Defense and an Elusivity defense bonus to Fire, Cold, Energy and Psionic Attacks in PVP zones. Recharge: Fast
Power_Shield.shortHelp: Toggle: Self +DEF(Fire, Cold, Energy, Negative), Res(DeBuff DEF)
Power_Shield.attackerHit: Your Power Shield increased your Defense to Fire, Cold, Energy and Negative Energy attacks.

Energize.help: You can channel a tremendous amount of energy through your body for a short period of time. Doing so will heal some hit points, reduce the endurance cost of your powers and boost your regeneration for a short time. Recharge: Very Long
Energize.attackerHit: You channel energy through your body healing you, making powers consume less endurance and boosting your regeneration rate.

Entropy_Shield.help: Entropy Shield diminishes and dampens the energy of controlling type effects. The shield makes you resistant to Knockback, Repel, Disorient, Hold, Sleep, Immobilization, and enemy Teleportation for as long as you can keep this toggle power active. Entropy Shield also grants you good resistance to Defense Debuffs. Additionally, this power grants the user a moderate recharge bonus while active and resistance to endurance drain effects. Recharge: Fast
Entropy_Shield.shortHelp: Toggle: Self +Res(Knockback, Repel, Disorient, Hold, Sleep, Immobilize, Teleport, DeBuff DEF), +Rech
Entropy_Shield.attackerHit: You are now highly resistant to Disorient, Immobilize, Hold, Sleep, Knockback, Repel, and enemy Teleportation.

Power_Armor.help: Power Armor increases your resistance to all damage types except Psionics or Toxic.
Power_Armor.attackerHit: Your Power Armor increased your Maximum Hit Points in addition to your Resistance to Smashing, Lethal, Fire, Cold, Energy and Negative Energy damage.

Repelling_Force.help: Your innate power over energies manifest itself naturally as a repelling force, increasing your defense against all types.

Power_Drain.help: Power Drain leeches energy directly from the bodies of all nearby foes, draining their Endurance. Each foe you draw energy from increases your Endurance. If there are no foes within range, you will not gain any Endurance. Recharge: Long

messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} steals some of your Endurance with a {PowerName}.
{PlayerSource} steals some of your Endurance with a {PowerName}.

Overload.help: You can Overload your Energy Aura and dramatically improve your defense to all attack types except Psionic Attacks. Overload also grants you high resistance to Defense Debuffs. This Energy Aura is so powerful, that it can even absorb some damage, effectively increasing your Max Hit Points. However, when Overload wears off, you are left drained of all Endurance and unable to recover Endurance for a while. Overload also adds a moderate Elusivity defense bonus to all attacks in PVP zones. Recharge: Very Long
Overload.shortHelp: Self +DEF(All but Psionics), +Recovery, +Max HP, Res(DeBuff DEF), +Special
Overload.attackerHit: You are Overloading your Energy Aura. You now have extreme Defense to all attacks except Psionics and your Max HP has been increased.

messages.attackerHit: {PowerName} has left you exhausted and unable to Recovery Endurance for a while!
